575
00:31:12,600 --> 00:31:13,159
Lying to the emperor?

576
00:31:15,479 --> 00:31:16,679
The crime of lying to the emperor?

577
00:31:17,551 --> 00:31:18,831
Does it mean you'll be beheaded?

578
00:31:21,719 --> 00:31:23,120
Aren't you worried about yourself?

579
00:31:23,979 --> 00:31:25,179
