582
00:31:28,360 --> 00:31:29,239
It's not easy

583
00:31:29,540 --> 00:31:30,919
to catch a loach in this huge world.

584
00:31:34,239 --> 00:31:35,219
However, I know

585
00:31:35,719 --> 00:31:36,800
I can't escape now.

586
00:31:40,519 --> 00:31:42,239
I want to ask you

587
00:31:42,719 --> 00:31:43,800
to pretend as my servant.

588
00:31:45,040 --> 00:31:46,120
Pretend as your servant?

589
00:31:46,540 --> 00:31:47,100
I know

590
00:31:47,239 --> 00:31:49,060
