655
00:34:24,800 --> 00:34:26,059
All of us overcame this.

656
00:34:28,999 --> 00:34:29,300
Your legs.

657
00:34:33,019 --> 00:34:33,559
Seriously.

658
00:34:38,439 --> 00:34:38,680
You...

659
00:34:39,119 --> 00:34:39,459
You...

660
00:34:40,059 --> 00:34:40,780
Sorry.

661
00:34:41,400 --> 00:34:41,919
Sorry.

662
