720
00:40:37,459 --> 00:40:39,280
As expected of
Marquis of Jianding Residence.

721
00:40:39,400 --> 00:40:42,160
Even a servant is so smart.

722
00:40:42,639 --> 00:40:43,499
All of you may leave.

723
00:40:48,240 --> 00:40:49,139
To be honest,

724
00:40:49,660 --> 00:40:51,559
I've always wanted to thank you

725
00:40:51,559 --> 00:40:53,079
for saving my life in person.

726
00:40:54,340 --> 00:40:55,439
There's no need to be so polite.

727
00:40:55,579 --> 00:40:56,539
It was what I should do.

728
00:40:58,180 --> 00:40:58,919
Not at all.

729
00:40:59,459 --> 00:41:01,300
Saving my life

730
00:41:01,539 --> 00:41:02,800
is the same as saving Wei.

731
00:41:03,519 --> 00:41:05,519
Moreover, I stay here temporarily

732
00:41:05,939 --> 00:41:06,820
