736
00:41:10,820 --> 00:41:12,039
You must come as well.

737
00:41:12,119 --> 00:41:12,419
All right?

738
00:41:13,160 --> 00:41:13,880
It's decided then.

739
00:41:16,619 --> 00:41:17,559
What a coincidence.

740
00:41:22,700 --> 00:41:23,300
Miss Jiang,

741
00:41:23,539 --> 00:41:24,240
